# CTA - Public Performance Pages (CTA-PPP)

macros and data to make plots for CTA-PPP

(root based)


# References and Sources

- LAT Pass 7 & 8: Philippe BRUEL talk at TeVPA
- HAWC: Abeysekaraa et al (HAWC collaboration) 2013
- MAGIC: Alecsik et al (MAGIC collaboration) 2014, Table 2 (Angular resolution), Fig 7 (effective area), Tab 5 (differential sensitivities)
- HESS: M.Holler et al (ICRC 2015)
- VERITAS: public performance page

